San Francisco Opera toasts to a new season in style|http://www.sfgate.com/music|https://datebook.sfchronicle.com/entertainment/live-chat-san-francisco-opera-ball-2018||2018-09-07|Chronicle Staff Report,Joshua Kosman||Welcome to The Chronicle’s gala-night live chat, featuring the Datebook and Style teams reporting live from the War Memorial Opera House. Tune in during the Opera Ball on Friday, Sept. 7, for updates from the red carpet, parties and more, including commentary on the opening-night double bill of “Cavalleria Rusticana” and “Pagliacci.”

The ball is chaired by Shannon Cronan and Kathy Huber. Proceeds from the evening benefit the Opera’s artistic, community and education programs.
